===2 For===
A type of price point in which two identical products are sold at a specified price. Not to be confused with [[BOGO.mediawiki|BOGO]].

=====Tooltip=====
Select "2 For" when the promotion features two products at a special price (i.e. 2 Egg McMuffin sandwiches for $3.33).

